title: Udemy - eBay Flipping 2018: The Fun Way To Serious Profit
description:
Description

Are you looking for a fun way to earn some extra income?Do you want to learn to “flip” inexpensive, easy to find items at a profit on eBay?Then you’re in the right place. My course “eBay Flipping 2018: The Fun Way To Serious Profit” is the course for you.

What is flipping and why you should do it?

Flipping is purchasing a revenue-generating asset and quickly reselling it for profit. The resale industry is big business. Huge, in fact. Thrift stores and antique store sales amount to billions of dollars in revenue each year. And the good news is that you can start it without having to set up a brick-and-mortar resale store of your own.

Who is the target audience?
    Anyone who has access to eBay and would like to learn a fun way to make some extra cash.

Requirements
    An Internet connected computer
    An eBay account
    A PayPal account
